<lb n="1"/>śrī jayavaruṣada śivayōga vini
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yamadi dhyānavanu māḍe dikkṛtisa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>hitaṁ sayadi sadāśivaliṁganu
</p>

